{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d7da24d71d","title":"陈伯达接见北京政法学院“政法公社”代表时的讲话","origin":"北京政法学院革命委员会《政法红旗》主办《红旗战报》第44期 1967年12月9日","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6171ffe187","index":0,"year":1967,"month":8,"day":23,"articleId":"d7da24d71d"}],"tags":[{"id":"145a049082","name":"天津文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e46e45351b","name":"陈伯达","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"48606ca4e5","name":"陈伯达"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c2a8714360","type":"title","text":"陈伯达接见北京政法学院“政法公社”代表时的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d7da24d71d"},{"id":"ccc3760c17","type":"authors","text":"陈伯达","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d7da24d71d"},{"id":"433828e98d","type":"paragraph","text":"八月二十三日凌晨，陈伯达同志在人大会堂召见北京《政法公社》代表时，说（摘要）：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d7da24d71d"},{"id":"e00d5cfac5","type":"paragraph","text":"“你们英雄！你们英雄！你们又一次想把我打成反革命。去年你们到天津小站去翻案，搞资本主义复辟。现在又去给《天津政法公社》翻案，这是复辟，是逆流。你们是搞专政的，你们是学国民党六法的，对我们进行专政，把我们打成反革命。”","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d7da24d71d"}],"page":{"id":"5e61477318","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d7da24d71d","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}